(47, 'B190305034', 'I am writing to express my extreme disappointment and frustration regarding the late delivery of an order I placed with your company. This delay has not only inconvenienced me but has also caused me to miss an important deadline that I was relying on. This situation is entirely unacceptable, and I am compelled to bring it to your attention.\r\n\r\n   When I made the purchase from your online store, I was provided with an estimated delivery date that I relied upon for planning. Unfortunately, that date came and went without any sign of the package. I had made arrangements and commitments based on the assumption that the order would arrive on time, and the delay has caused me significant problems both personally and professionally.\r\n\r\n   Time-sensitive commitments are a common aspect of life, and customers rely on accurate delivery estimates to make informed decisions. In this case, your company&#039;s failure to meet its own promised timeline has resulted in tangible consequences for me.\r\n\r\n   I expect an immediate explanation for the cause of the delay and a commitment to ensuring that such delays do not occur in the future. Additionally, I demand appropriate compensation for the inconvenience and the negative impact this situation has had on my schedule and commitments.\r\n\r\n   It&#039;s important to acknowledge that reliable and punctual delivery is a key factor in customer satisfaction. I hope that this complaint prompts your company to take a closer look at its logistics and delivery processes to prevent such instances from occurring in the future.', '169255449213.jpg', 21, 0, 15, 'Request: R-', 'Request', '2023-08-20 18:01:32', 'Approved', ''),
