(50, 'B190305035', 'I am writing to express my disappointment and frustration with the recent purchase I made from your company. The product I received is drastically different from the one described on your website, and this misrepresentation has left me feeling misled and dissatisfied as a customer.\r\n\r\n   When I made the purchase, I carefully reviewed the product description and images provided on your website to ensure that it met my needs and expectations. However, upon receiving the product, I was shocked to find that it did not match the description at all. The size, color, and features of the item were all different from what was advertised.\r\n\r\n   This situation is not only frustrating but also a waste of my time and money. I chose your company over others based on the information you provided, and it&#039;s disheartening to think that this information was inaccurate or misleading.\r\n\r\n   I insist on a resolution to this matter. I demand a full refund for the purchase and any associated shipping costs. Additionally, I encourage your company to take a closer look at its product listings to ensure that they are accurate and reflective of the actual items being sold.\r\n\r\n   Trust is a fundamental aspect of any customer-brand relationship. In this\r\n\r\n case, that trust has been compromised due to the mismatch between the advertised product and the one I received. I hope that you take this feedback seriously and use it as an opportunity to improve your product representation and customer experience.', '169255618012.jpg', 13, 0, 26, 'Complain: C-', 'Complain', '2023-08-20 18:29:40', 'Approved', 'We have received your complain. Your complain will be resolved as soon as possible.'),
